[Episode 4]

4
00:02:36,100 --> 00:02:36,620
Is this your place?

5
00:02:37,660 --> 00:02:38,180
No,

6
00:02:38,780 --> 00:02:39,460
I'm waiting for someone.

7
00:02:40,500 --> 00:02:41,460
Who are you trying to fool?

8
00:02:42,620 --> 00:02:43,140
Where's Qi Lian?

9
00:03:13,260 --> 00:03:14,180
So you're Qi Lian, huh?

10
00:03:15,700 --> 00:03:17,140
You really gave our boss a hard time.

11
00:03:17,340 --> 00:03:18,620
I can't let you off without a lesson,

12
00:03:19,100 --> 00:03:19,740
or you won't even remember

13
00:03:19,740 --> 00:03:20,460
your own name.

14
00:03:42,620 --> 00:03:43,060
Get lost!

15
00:04:19,860 --> 00:04:20,940
Aren't you here to repay the money?

16
00:04:27,900 --> 00:04:28,660
Here's your 200.

17
00:04:29,180 --> 00:04:29,780
Just let me go.

18
00:04:32,540 --> 00:04:33,220
Are you afraid of me?

19
00:04:40,180 --> 00:04:40,620
Not at all.

20
00:04:40,980 --> 00:04:41,700
Why would I be?

21
00:04:44,820 --> 00:04:45,540
Do you think

22
00:04:45,580 --> 00:04:47,020
I'm like those thugs?

23
00:04:52,020 --> 00:04:53,700
I'm just investing in small businesses

24
00:04:54,100 --> 00:04:55,460
and doing some We-Media work.

25
00:04:57,380 --> 00:04:59,140
A contractor owed people wages

26
00:04:59,820 --> 00:05:00,900
got reported by me.

27
00:05:01,460 --> 00:05:02,100
Those guys

28
00:05:02,140 --> 00:05:02,820
were sent by the contractor

29
00:05:03,700 --> 00:05:04,820
just to scare me.

30
00:05:10,460 --> 00:05:11,020
Come with me.

31
00:05:11,380 --> 00:05:11,940
Come inside and sit.

32
00:05:34,140 --> 00:05:35,140
I didn't...

33
00:05:40,020 --> 00:05:40,900
mean to.

34
00:06:00,300 --> 00:06:00,780
Sit down.

35
00:06:08,020 --> 00:06:08,380
Well,

36
00:06:08,900 --> 00:06:09,580
by the way,

37
00:06:11,340 --> 00:06:12,540
A friend at the hospital told me

38
00:06:12,860 --> 00:06:13,820
that Ms. Zhang's subsequent bills

39
00:06:13,820 --> 00:06:14,860
will be compensated
by the insurance company.

40
00:06:16,020 --> 00:06:17,020
You don't need to worry about it.

41
00:06:26,860 --> 00:06:27,420
Do you want some water?

42
00:06:33,820 --> 00:06:34,260
I...

43
00:06:34,620 --> 00:06:35,180
I'm not thirsty.

44
00:06:36,660 --> 00:06:37,300
There's water on the table.

45
00:06:41,460 --> 00:06:42,980
(Why did I even come in here?)

46
00:06:43,780 --> 00:06:45,100
(I was just here to repay the money.)

47
00:06:46,300 --> 00:06:46,660
(Right,)

48
00:06:47,300 --> 00:06:48,140
(I've paid back the money,)

49
00:06:49,740 --> 00:06:50,820
(I can't stay here any longer.)

50
00:06:54,340 --> 00:06:54,980
Well,

51
00:06:55,420 --> 00:06:56,540
I just came to repay you.

52
00:06:57,460 --> 00:06:58,380
The money's paid off.

53
00:06:58,460 --> 00:06:59,060
I should be going now.

54
00:07:01,220 --> 00:07:02,260
Do you want some rice with curry?

55
00:08:30,020 --> 00:08:31,020
(This guy)

56
00:08:31,700 --> 00:08:32,420
(doesn't seem)

57
00:08:32,460 --> 00:08:33,460
(as scary as I thought.)

58
00:08:47,020 --> 00:08:49,140
(Maybe it's just a friendly gesture)

59
00:08:49,460 --> 00:08:50,740
(since we come from the same village.)

60
00:10:05,940 --> 00:10:07,140
(Why does he keep so many photos)

61
00:10:07,140 --> 00:10:08,660
(of corpses in his house?)

62
00:10:09,700 --> 00:10:11,020
(I must have been out of my mind)

63
00:10:11,020 --> 00:10:12,220
(to stay here for a meal.)

64
00:10:12,540 --> 00:10:13,340
(If I don't escape now,)

65
00:10:13,340 --> 00:10:14,060
(I'm doomed.)

66
00:10:25,060 --> 00:10:25,620
Jiang Xiaoyuan,

67
00:10:26,260 --> 00:10:26,900
where are you going?

68
00:10:27,740 --> 00:10:29,300
We met by chance and got acquainted.

69
00:10:29,500 --> 00:10:30,340
Thanks for helping me.

70
00:10:30,380 --> 00:10:31,300
Hope we meet again if fate allows.

71
00:10:35,020 --> 00:10:36,420
Meeting by chance?

72
00:10:37,340 --> 00:10:38,300
Help!

73
00:10:38,420 --> 00:10:39,580
Someone's harassing me!

74
00:10:40,340 --> 00:10:41,460
Help!

75
00:10:41,820 --> 00:10:43,100
Help, please!

76
00:10:44,060 --> 00:10:44,780
Help!

77
00:10:49,780 --> 00:10:50,300
Shut up.

78
00:10:51,860 --> 00:10:52,980
If you don't want to die,

79
00:10:53,060 --> 00:10:53,980
just follow me quietly.

80
00:11:01,300 --> 00:11:03,980
♪Now every time I can feel the wind♪

81
00:11:04,020 --> 00:11:07,140
