82
00:11:07,580 --> 00:11:10,340
♪No need to tell me what to do♪

83
00:11:10,380 --> 00:11:13,820
♪In this rush, I feel, I see♪

84
00:11:13,900 --> 00:11:16,220
♪Just let me flow♪

85
00:11:16,460 --> 00:11:18,620
♪Feeling the pull of time and space♪

86
00:11:18,780 --> 00:11:21,140
♪Clutching the wind in my grasp♪

87
00:11:21,140 --> 00:11:22,860
♪On paths untrodden♪

88
00:11:23,700 --> 00:11:25,620
♪We don't have to wait for the light♪

89
00:11:25,620 --> 00:11:27,220
♪My rhythm♪

90
00:11:27,220 --> 00:11:29,060
♪Just let me flow♪

91
00:11:29,100 --> 00:11:31,460
♪Until I become a wind too♪

92
00:11:31,460 --> 00:11:33,820
♪I'll blow away reality's weight♪

93
00:11:33,820 --> 00:11:35,580
♪Towards skies bright♪

94
00:11:36,420 --> 00:11:38,060
♪In the vast dreamscape♪

95
00:11:38,060 --> 00:11:39,900
♪My rhythm♪

96
