[Fashion Hairdressing Salon]

97
00:11:44,500 --> 00:11:44,980
You are here.

98
00:11:50,140 --> 00:11:50,780
Still the same.

99
00:11:51,980 --> 00:11:52,660
I'm leaving her in your care.

100
00:11:56,620 --> 00:11:57,540
And you're leaving just like that?

101
00:12:00,420 --> 00:12:00,980
Xiaoyuan,

102
00:12:01,700 --> 00:12:03,060
Qi Lian told me everything about you.

103
00:12:03,740 --> 00:12:04,460
You're looking for a job, right?

104
00:12:04,820 --> 00:12:05,780
It just so happens
I need help at my salon.

105
00:12:06,500 --> 00:12:07,420
It's pretty good here.

106
00:12:07,940 --> 00:12:08,500
And as an old acquaintance,

107
00:12:08,540 --> 00:12:09,380
I'll watch over you.

108
00:12:09,820 --> 00:12:10,220
What do you think?

109
00:12:11,580 --> 00:12:12,420
Do I know you that well?

110
00:12:14,420 --> 00:12:15,100
No way.

111
00:12:15,740 --> 00:12:16,460
Jiang Xiaoyuan!

112
00:12:17,140 --> 00:12:18,500
You can't recognize me just because

113
00:12:18,620 --> 00:12:19,620
you've been in a big city for years?

114
00:12:22,900 --> 00:12:23,340
I am

115
00:12:23,980 --> 00:12:24,620
Chen Fangzhou.

116
00:12:25,220 --> 00:12:25,860
Zhou.

117
00:12:28,500 --> 00:12:30,060
Is it because I've become so handsome

118
00:12:30,540 --> 00:12:31,620
that you're afraid

119
00:12:32,500 --> 00:12:33,980
to admit that you know me?

120
00:12:36,780 --> 00:12:37,300
Alright then.

121
00:12:39,180 --> 00:12:40,420
We used to be classmates.

122
00:12:40,620 --> 00:12:41,540
Now that you're in trouble,

123
00:12:41,740 --> 00:12:42,580
I should

124
00:12:42,580 --> 00:12:43,420
help you out anyway.

125
00:12:44,020 --> 00:12:44,420
Come on,

126
00:12:44,620 --> 00:12:45,580
let me show you around.

127
00:12:58,220 --> 00:12:59,540
Hello, boss.

128
00:12:59,860 --> 00:13:01,260
This is our lobby.

129
00:13:01,580 --> 00:13:03,020
Our lobby features

130
00:13:03,340 --> 00:13:05,300
European-style luxury architecture.

131
00:13:05,900 --> 00:13:07,260
After greeting the clients in the lobby,

132
00:13:07,740 --> 00:13:08,900
we usually take them straight
to the shampoo area.

133
00:13:09,140 --> 00:13:09,900
Usually on the way there,

134
00:13:10,100 --> 00:13:11,180
we'll find out what they need.

135
00:13:11,700 --> 00:13:12,300
Follow me.

136
00:13:14,260 --> 00:13:14,740
This

137
00:13:15,260 --> 00:13:16,900
is our shampoo area.

138
00:13:17,180 --> 00:13:18,460
We have a total

139
00:13:18,780 --> 00:13:20,620
of one, two, three, six

140
00:13:20,900 --> 00:13:22,140
luxurious stations.

141
00:13:22,980 --> 00:13:25,380
This is our hairdressing area.

142
00:13:25,500 --> 00:13:26,820
We have

143
00:13:26,900 --> 00:13:28,060
eight hairdressers

144
00:13:28,340 --> 00:13:29,140
providing services

145
00:13:29,260 --> 00:13:30,300
on rotation everyday.

146
00:13:30,660 --> 00:13:31,860
Hello, boss.

147
00:13:32,060 --> 00:13:32,380
Good.

148
00:13:32,620 --> 00:13:33,140
Get to work then.

149
00:13:33,620 --> 00:13:34,180
Of course.

150
00:13:34,540 --> 00:13:35,940
Senior hairdressers

151
00:13:36,340 --> 00:13:37,380
usually serve clients

152
00:13:37,460 --> 00:13:38,900
in private rooms.

153
00:13:40,780 --> 00:13:41,540
I am one of them.

154
00:13:47,660 --> 00:13:48,300
So

155
00:13:48,580 --> 00:13:50,060
our salon is a comprehensive hair salon

156
00:13:50,260 --> 00:13:51,980
that offers

157
00:13:52,180 --> 00:13:52,980
washing,

158
00:13:53,100 --> 00:13:54,060
cutting, blow-drying,

159
00:13:54,340 --> 00:13:56,380
perming, and dyeing.

160
00:14:02,940 --> 00:14:05,060
If you decide to stay,

161
00:14:05,700 --> 00:14:06,780
you'll start as an apprentice.

162
00:14:07,140 --> 00:14:07,700
Of course,

163
00:14:08,340 --> 00:14:09,860
initial salary won't be too high.

164
00:14:10,260 --> 00:14:11,260
The base is 2,000,

165
00:14:11,820 --> 00:14:13,260
but there are weekly quizzes

166
00:14:13,460 --> 00:14:14,340
and monthly exams.

167
00:14:14,580 --> 00:14:15,380
As your rank increases,

168
00:14:15,700 --> 00:14:16,860
so will your salary.

169
00:14:17,340 --> 00:14:18,620
Besides base pay,

170
00:14:18,660 --> 00:14:19,700
there's also performance bonus.

171
00:14:19,980 --> 00:14:21,060
Work hard, be diligent

172
00:14:21,540 --> 00:14:23,380
and you might earn over 7,000 a month

173
00:14:23,780 --> 00:14:24,900
in a year.

174
00:14:33,820 --> 00:14:35,460
You have no place to stay.

175
00:14:36,300 --> 00:14:37,060
Anyway,

176
00:14:37,140 --> 00:14:38,300
you need a job.

177
00:14:39,420 --> 00:14:39,940
So why not

178
00:14:41,100 --> 00:14:41,740
consider it?

179
00:14:42,940 --> 00:14:43,660
Are meals included?

180
00:14:43,940 --> 00:14:44,860
Yes.

181
00:15:07,540 --> 00:15:08,180
Here's your uniform.

182
00:15:08,580 --> 00:15:09,300
Wear it

183
00:15:09,340 --> 00:15:10,020
when working.

184
00:15:10,940 --> 00:15:11,500
Helen,

185
00:15:13,340 --> 00:15:14,340
this is a friend from my hometown.

186
00:15:14,780 --> 00:15:15,540
Please take care of her.

187
00:15:16,500 --> 00:15:17,260
This is Helen.

188
00:15:24,060 --> 00:15:25,260
Pretty, isn't she?

189
00:15:28,460 --> 00:15:29,460
Is she your friend from your hometown

190
00:15:29,700 --> 00:15:30,820
or your girlfriend?

191
00:15:31,980 --> 00:15:32,980
Cut it out.

192
00:15:33,180 --> 00:15:34,460
Stop gossiping.

193
00:15:34,820 --> 00:15:36,380
You're like some kind of gossip guru,

194
00:15:36,500 --> 00:15:37,580
always so nosy!

195
00:15:42,580 --> 00:15:43,060
Helen is

196
00:15:43,460 --> 00:15:44,980
our hairdressing supervisor here.

197
00:15:45,220 --> 00:15:45,700
She's like that.

198
00:15:46,220 --> 00:15:47,140
You'll get used to her.

199
00:15:48,780 --> 00:15:50,100
A supervisor's no match for the boss.

200
00:15:51,060 --> 00:15:52,300
She acts all high and mighty
in front of you.

201
00:15:52,300 --> 00:15:53,660
She doesn't take you seriously.

202
00:15:53,900 --> 00:15:55,260
You're one to talk.

203
00:15:55,500 --> 00:15:56,100
You don't treat me

204
00:15:56,140 --> 00:15:56,940
with much respect either.

205
00:15:57,420 --> 00:15:58,500
At least she's skilled.

206
00:15:59,220 --> 00:15:59,940
Learn from her.

207
00:16:00,860 --> 00:16:01,500
From now on,

208
00:16:01,540 --> 00:16:02,500
she'll be your direct supervisor.

209
00:16:02,780 --> 00:16:03,300
Be careful

210
00:16:03,700 --> 00:16:04,340
not to clash with her.

211
00:16:06,220 --> 00:16:06,620
Alright,

212
00:16:06,740 --> 00:16:07,820
stop sitting around.

213
00:16:08,180 --> 00:16:09,180
Let me take you to the dormitory

214
00:16:09,220 --> 00:16:09,820
and get you settled.

215
00:16:09,980 --> 00:16:10,580
Let's go.

216
00:16:13,460 --> 00:16:15,540
What's so great
about being a supervisor?

217
00:16:32,340 --> 00:16:33,260
[Investigation on Jiang Xiaoyuan]

218
00:16:33,260 --> 00:16:34,580
(During those years in Chongqing,
Jiang Xiaoyuan)

219
00:16:34,580 --> 00:16:35,380
(didn't have it easy.)

220
00:16:35,900 --> 00:16:37,020
(Her classmates said)

221
00:16:37,100 --> 00:16:38,580
(she'd started working part-time
since she went to school)

222
00:16:38,940 --> 00:16:40,060
(and rarely socialized with others.)

223
00:16:43,100 --> 00:16:43,820
(Somehow)

224
00:16:43,940 --> 00:16:44,580
(she offended)

225
00:16:44,580 --> 00:16:45,860
(some powerful
and influential classmate.)

226
00:16:46,100 --> 00:16:47,260
(As a result,
she was extremely unpopular.)

227
00:16:47,620 --> 00:16:49,260
(Afterwards, there was no news about her.)

228
00:16:50,180 --> 00:16:51,060
(Jiang Xiaoyuan,)

229
00:16:54,020 --> 00:16:55,100
(why didn't you come to find me)

230
00:16:55,100 --> 00:16:56,060
(all these years?)

231
00:17:05,340 --> 00:17:05,780
Come in.

232
00:17:08,380 --> 00:17:08,980
This is

233
00:17:09,020 --> 00:17:10,340
our hair salon's employee dormitory.

234
00:17:14,500 --> 00:17:15,260
You'll stay in this room.

235
00:17:16,660 --> 00:17:17,740
You and Li will share a room.

236
00:17:20,020 --> 00:17:21,100
Try to get some rest early.

237
00:17:21,740 --> 00:17:22,500
Set an alarm clock.

238
00:17:22,740 --> 00:17:23,660
Work starts at nine tomorrow.

239
00:17:24,620 --> 00:17:25,900
You don't look well-rested.

240
00:17:26,500 --> 00:17:27,500
Qi Lian said he's been busy lately,

241
00:17:27,780 --> 00:17:28,900
but he'll come to see you when he's free.

242
00:17:29,860 --> 00:17:30,980
Why would he come to see me?

243
00:17:31,140 --> 00:17:32,140
Don't play dumb.

244
00:17:35,140 --> 00:17:36,020
He probably thinks

245
00:17:36,020 --> 00:17:37,140
he should look after me

246
00:17:37,380 --> 00:17:38,660
since we're from the same town.

247
00:17:39,780 --> 00:17:40,780
But I think

248
00:17:40,780 --> 00:17:41,660
he's a bit dangerous.

249
00:17:42,140 --> 00:17:43,220
And I already told him,

250
00:17:43,220 --> 00:17:44,260
I don't need his help.

251
00:17:44,780 --> 00:17:45,260
Wait.

252
00:17:46,740 --> 00:17:47,660
Don't you really remember?

253
00:17:48,260 --> 00:17:49,220
You and Qi Lian were so close

254
00:17:49,220 --> 00:17:50,140
back then.

255
00:17:50,500 --> 00:17:51,860
You were always together.

256
00:17:52,660 --> 00:17:54,140
Then you went to university in Chongqing

257
00:17:54,260 --> 00:17:55,540
without even telling him.

258
00:17:55,740 --> 00:17:57,100
He was heartbroken for so long.

259
00:17:57,460 --> 00:17:58,660
Now you're finally back

260
00:17:58,980 --> 00:18:00,340
but acting like you don't know him.

261
00:18:01,140 --> 00:18:02,100
If there's some issue between you two,

262
00:18:02,100 --> 00:18:02,860
why not just talk it out

263
00:18:02,900 --> 00:18:03,660
face-to-face?

264
00:18:04,260 --> 00:18:05,660
Why should you hurt him like this?

265
00:18:07,860 --> 00:18:09,140
I haven't seen Qi Lian caring

266
00:18:09,140 --> 00:18:10,500
for someone so much for years.

267
00:18:15,260 --> 00:18:16,020
Get some rest early.

268
00:18:18,740 --> 00:18:19,860
And remember to set an alarm.

269
00:18:53,500 --> 00:18:54,460
(This hair salon)

270
00:18:54,460 --> 00:18:55,740
(seems to be quite decent.)

271
00:18:56,500 --> 00:18:57,340
(Definitely more legitimate)

272
00:18:57,460 --> 00:18:58,300
(than that shady internet cafe.)

273
00:18:59,580 --> 00:19:00,420
(I'll try)

274
00:19:00,460 --> 00:19:01,260
(to survive for now.)

275
00:19:02,020 --> 00:19:02,660
(Jiang Xiaoyuan.)

276
00:19:09,060 --> 00:19:09,820
Give it back.

277
00:19:26,500 --> 00:19:28,060
(When one hits rock bottom,)

278
00:19:28,540 --> 00:19:29,980
(it's not impossible
to come across a kind soul)

279
00:19:29,980 --> 00:19:31,300
(or two who would lend a hand.)

280
00:19:32,460 --> 00:19:33,820
(Let's take it slow for now.)

281
00:19:34,260 --> 00:19:34,980
(Be brave.)

282
00:19:35,500 --> 00:19:36,340
(There's always a way out.)

