00:19:55,460 --> 00:20:01,740
[Fashion Hairdressing Salon]

284
00:20:11,220 --> 00:20:11,780
Stop right there!

285
00:20:14,260 --> 00:20:14,820
What time is it?

286
00:20:16,060 --> 00:20:16,940
Why are you late

287
00:20:17,020 --> 00:20:17,740
on your first day of work?

288
00:20:18,100 --> 00:20:18,780
Didn't I remind you yesterday

289
00:20:18,820 --> 00:20:19,540
to set an alarm clock?

