322
00:22:24,140 --> 00:22:24,940
Come with me for a sec.

323
00:22:30,220 --> 00:22:31,020
Here's a lunchbox.

324
00:22:31,220 --> 00:22:31,860
Eat up.

325
00:22:49,340 --> 00:22:50,260
Xiaoyuan,

326
